 axe as a walking stick, a rucksack that always had stuff hanging out of it and held a . He hardly ever bathed, but he was welcomed by everyone as they knew him as a captivating storyteller. 

According to himself he had met both Jutul (a type of giant) and the hulder who tried to seduce him. He married a widow 24 years older than him, who was known for her physical strength. On the day of their wedding, she that carried him over a river they had to cross to get to the church, to the amusement of the locals. 

Some of his stories was documented by Ingebret Moltke Moe, son of Jørgen Moe who gathered stories that you might know like "Three Billy Goats Gruff" and "Chicken Little".

Eilev Bråtene died in 1899 when the 70 year old lost his footing and fell into a river. The newspaper obituary described him as an (roughly translated) "old weirdo".</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/i66CsxZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheAnswerWasAlwaysMoreLube]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I heard it was mug day</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ACe8RuW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/61JHknq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Edit: Imgur apparently doesn’t appreciate this post and removed the #mug tag and instead added the politics tag. Sounds like Imgur thinks these people being arraigned is a political issue.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ACe8RuW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SLCtechie]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Reading is fundamental</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aPqjm4Z</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XHxlMlw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aPqjm4Z</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jacobblanck2000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Irony</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MsFqDYd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8SQd8WV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MsFqDYd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vodray]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Dino Transformer</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Dma6Gsb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wKi8wpV.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Dma6Gsb</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[exploradoresciclos2018]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Thank you human for your kindness.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PjZj0Zw</link><de